languages.text: "Такой перстенек славный был, куда же делся? Если найду да господину блюстителю подам, авось отпустит за службу добрую... Точно отпустят..."
"It was such a nice ring, but where did it go? If I find it, I'll give it back to them, and then maybe they'll let me go for my good service... I'm sure they will..."

languages.text: « C'était une si belle bague... Où a-t-elle bien pu passer ? Si je la retrouve, je la lui rendrai, et peut-être qu'alors, il acceptera de me relâcher... Oui, il devrait me relâcher... »

languages.text: "Der Ring war hübsch, aber wo ist er geblieben? Falls ich ihn finde, gebe ich ihn zurück, dann lassen sie mich als Dank vielleicht gehen ... Ja, das werden sie bestimmt."

languages.text: «Era un bonito anillo, ¿dónde estará? Si lo encuentro y se lo devuelvo, igual me dejan ir por buena conducta... Seguro...».

languages.text: 「すごく素敵な指輪だったんだけど、どこに行ってしまったんだろう？もし見つかったらお返ししますよ。もしかすると、その善行に免じて解放してくれるかもしれない。きっとそうしてくれるはず…」
languages.original_text: "It was such a nice ring, but where did it go? If I find it, I'll give it back to them, and then maybe they'll let me go for my good service... I'm sure they will..."

languages.text: “那个戒指确实很漂亮，但到底掉哪去了？要是我捡到的话，我会还给他们，这样他们说不定会因为我配合而放我走……我相信他们会这么做……”
languages.original_text: "It was such a nice ring, but where did it go? If I find it, I'll give it back to them, and then maybe they'll let me go for my good service... I'm sure they will..."

languages.text: "Çok güzel bir yüzüktü ama nereye gitti? Bulursam ona geri veririm. Böylece iyi hizmet ettiğim için belki gitmeme müsaade eder. Edeceğine eminim..."
languages.original_text: "It was such a nice ring, but where did it go? If I find it, I'll give it back to them, and then maybe they'll let me go for my good service... I'm sure they will..."
